NỘI DUNG CHÍNH
────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

  • Command Line Shortcuts
      • Ctrl + a : Move to beginning of line
      • Ctrl + e : Move to end of line
      • !! : Repeat last command
      • ESC + . : Repeat last argument
      • cd - : Toggle previous directory
      • Ctrl + r : Search command history

  • File Operations
      • mkdir, cd, ls
      • cp, mv (move/rename), rm
      • Aliases (alias, unalias)

  • Editing Files
      • nano, vim
      • sed (stream editor)

  • Other
      • diff (compare files)
      • Redirection, piping


